Transforms

dat2 <- within(dat2, {
  tr3_AxisLen <- AxisLen
  tr3_FemShACT <- 5 * log(FemShACT)
  tr3_FemShBR <- 5 * log(FemShBR)
  tr3_FemShCSA <- FemShCSA
  tr3_FemShCSMI <- 7 * log(FemShCSMI + median(FemShCSMI, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_FemShSMod <- 30 * log(FemShSMod + 5 * median(FemShSMod, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_HipTotBMD <- 8 * HipTotBMD
  tr3_InterBMD <- 7 * InterBMD
  tr3_IntTrACT <- 11 * log(IntTrACT + median(IntTrACT, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_IntTrBR <- 10 * log(IntTrBR + 0.01 * median(IntTrBR, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_IntTrCSA <- log(IntTrCSA + median(IntTrCSA, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_IntTrCSMI <- 7 * log(IntTrCSMI + median(IntTrCSMI, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_IntTrSMod <- 8 * log(IntTrSMod + median(IntTrSMod, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_NeckBMD <- 13 * log(NeckBMD + median(NeckBMD, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_NNeckACT <- 13 * log(NNeckACT + median(NNeckACT, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_NNeckBR <- 10 * log(NNeckBR + median(NNeckBR, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_NNeckCSA <- 11 * log(NNeckCSA + median(NNeckCSA, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_NNeckCSMI <- 7 * log(NNeckCSMI + median(NNeckCSMI, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_NNeckSMod <- 9 * log(NNeckSMod + median(NNeckSMod, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_ShaftNeck <- ShaftNeck
  tr3_TotBMD <- 12 * log(TotBMD + median(TotBMD, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_TrochBMD <- 14 * log(TrochBMD + median(TrochBMD, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_WBTotArea <- 18 * log(WBTotArea + median(WBTotArea, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_WBTotBMC <- WBTotBMC
  tr3_WBTotBMD <- 19 * log(WBTotBMD + median(WBTotBMD, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_WBTotFat <- 7 * log(WBTotFat + median(WBTotFat, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_WBTotLean <- WBTotLean
  tr3_HydVitD <- 3 * log(HydVitD + 0.01 * median(HydVitD, na.rm = TRUE))
  # 1 outlier
  stopifnot(sum(tr3_HydVitD > 13.5, na.rm = TRUE) == 1)
  tr3_HydVitD[tr3_HydVitD > 13.5] <- NA 
  tr3_Sclerostin <- 7 * log(Sclerostin)
  # 2 outliers
  stopifnot(sum(tr3_Sclerostin > 30, na.rm = TRUE) == 1)
  tr3_Sclerostin[tr3_Sclerostin > 30] <- NA 
  stopifnot(sum(tr3_Sclerostin < 17, na.rm = TRUE) == 1)
  tr3_Sclerostin[tr3_Sclerostin < 17] <- NA 
  tr3_SerCrossLaps <- log(SerCrossLaps)
  tr3_OstaseBAP <- log(OstaseBAP)
  tr3_IGF1 <- 5 * log(IGF1 + median(IGF1, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_Adiponectin <- log(Adiponectin)
  # 1 outlier
  stopifnot(sum(tr3_Adiponectin < 14.5, na.rm = TRUE) == 1)
  tr3_Adiponectin[tr3_Adiponectin < 14.5] <- NA 
  tr3_Leptin <- log(Leptin + 0.05 * median(Leptin, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_Osteocalcin <- log(Osteocalcin + 0.1 * median(Osteocalcin, na.rm = TRUE))
  # 1 outliers
  stopifnot(sum(tr3_Osteocalcin < 7.5, na.rm = TRUE) == 1)
  tr3_Osteocalcin[tr3_Osteocalcin < 7.5] <- NA 
  tr3_Osteoprotegerin <- 3 * log(Osteoprotegerin)
  # 1 outliers
  stopifnot(sum(tr3_Osteoprotegerin < 10, na.rm = TRUE) == 1)
  tr3_Osteoprotegerin[tr3_Osteoprotegerin < 10] <- NA 
  tr3_Osteopontin <- log(Osteopontin)
  # 1 outliers
  stopifnot(sum(tr3_Osteopontin < 6, na.rm = TRUE) == 1)
  tr3_Osteopontin[tr3_Osteopontin < 6] <- NA 
  tr3_Parathyroid <- log(Parathyroid)
  tr3_TNFalpha <- log(TNFalpha)
  ### 
  tr3_BMI <- 8 * log(BMI + 0.01 * median(BMI, na.rm = TRUE))
  #tr3_Height <- 40 * log(Height + median(Height, na.rm = TRUE))
  tr3_Height <- Height
  tr3_Weight <- Weight
})
